Real Perfection 16 pcs Pink Makeup Brush Set Includes: 1. Angled Blush Brush, 2. Flat Angled Foundation, 3. Powder Brush, 4. Face Flat Brush, 5. Tapered Brush, 6. Angled Shading Brush, 7. Eyeliner Brush, 17. Eyebrow Razor(Free Gift & Random Color)

Steps for Cleaning Makeup Brushes: 1. Wet the bristles in warm water, please do not use hot water as the heat might damage the bristles. 2. Pour some mild cleanser (like baby shampoo) into the water, stir the mixture gently to combine. 3. Only dip the bottom half of the brush into the mixture and swirl the bristles in the water until the brush is fully lathered. Note: Do not fully immerse the whole base of the bristles to avoid water traveling up the handle. 4. Rinse the bristles, squeeze the water out of the bristles gently. 5. Repeat the above steps until all cosmetics are removed. 6. Reshape the bristles, let the brush air-dry, then fluff it with your fingers.

Premium Material Makeup Brushes High-quality wood handle with a durable aluminum ferrule, together they provide a nice grip and hold the bristles firmly, no shedding while applying makeup. Hold Makeup Products Wonderfully 100% vegan and cruelty-free bristles are super soft and dense, can pick up products and dispense them as you wish. Eyebrow Razor (Random Color) Perfect for shaping eyebrows, removing fine hairs, and even smoothening skin.

reviews.reviewText: The Real Perfection 16pcs Makeup Brushes Set is a comprehensive collection of brushes designed to meet all your makeup application needs. With a variety of brush types and a bonus eyebrow razor, this set offers versatility, quality, and convenience for both beginners and makeup enthusiasts.One of the standout features of this brush set is its variety and range of brush types. It includes brushes for all aspects of makeup application, from foundation and concealer to eyeshadow and blush. The set even includes specialized brushes for more precise tasks like eyeliner and brows. This comprehensive selection allows you to achieve a professional finish and experiment with different makeup looks. In conclusion, the Real Perfection 16pcs Makeup Brushes Set is a comprehensive and versatile collection that provides excellent value for its price. The brushes are made with high-quality synthetic bristles, ensuring effective product application and easy maintenance. The inclusion of a bonus eyebrow razor adds to the convenience and versatility of the set. Whether you're a beginner or a makeup enthusiast, this brush set is a worthy addition to your beauty arsenal.
